                  <msItem>
                     <p>
                        <pb n="435"/> Convention made in the village of <placeName key="place_104540">St. Edmund</placeName>, in full 
                  "portmaneiot", before <persName>
                           <forename>Adam</forename> de
                     <surname>Phalelham</surname>
                        </persName> then provost, and others, by which
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Isabella</forename>, daughter of <persName>
                              <forename>Walter</forename> 
                              <surname>Gochep</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, 
                  gave to the brethren of the <orgName key="org_105024">hospital of St. Peter</orgName>, for five marks one acre of 
                  arable land opposite the hospital in the fields of <placeName key="place_104540">St. Edmund</placeName>, in exchange for one
                  acre of arable land with a meadow adjacent in the fields of the same vill, "extra portam del Su", viz.
                  that which <persName>master <forename>Abbraham</forename>
                        </persName> gave to the said brethren 
                  of St. Peter in frankalmoigne.
                     (<origDate notBefore="1210" notAfter="1220" precision="low">c. 1210-20</origDate>.)
                     </p>
